videos.description: South Carolina takes an early 7-0 lead over Tennessee as Kevin Harris makes an all-out dive for the pylon to reach the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris dives to score short Gamecocks' TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris dives to score short Gamecocks' TD

videos.description: Collin Hill has his pass picked off by Henry To'o To'o who returns it 32 yards for a Tennessee touchdown as they take a 14-7 lead over South Carolina.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Volunteers defense comes up with pick-6) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Volunteers defense comes up with pick-6

videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano lobs a deep pass to Brandon Johnson, who stretches out to make a one-handed grab along the sideline with a defender draped all over him.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Johnson makes sweet one-handed grab along the sideline) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnson makes sweet one-handed grab along the sideline

videos.description: Collin Hill throws a strike to Shi Smith in the middle of the field, and Smith makes a big leap into the end zone to score a 29-yard touchdown for the Gamecocks.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hill connects with Smith for 29-yard South Carolina TD) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hill connects with Smith for 29-yard South Carolina TD

videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano perfectly leads Josh Palmer to the end zone with a 32-yard pass as Tennessee retakes the lead over South Carolina 31-24.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Guarantano finds Palmer for 32-yard Tennessee score) 2020/09/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Guarantano finds Palmer for 32-yard Tennessee score

videos.description: No. 16 Tennessee extends its win streak to seven games, defeating South Carolina 31-27 with success on both sides of the ball.
videos.headline: Vols maintain 2019 momentum with season-opening win
